sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant StreamlitApp
    participant AgentGraph
    participant Tools
    participant XRPL
    participant Webhook
    participant SQLiteDB
    participant Ollama

    User->>StreamlitApp: Load dashboard
    StreamlitApp->>SQLiteDB: fetch transaction history
    StreamlitApp->>Config: load settings
    StreamlitApp->>AgentGraph: prepare workflow config

    User->>StreamlitApp: Run Multi-Agent Cycle
    StreamlitApp->>AgentGraph: stream(initial_state)

    AgentGraph->>Ollama: procurement decision
    Ollama-->>AgentGraph: procurement result
    AgentGraph->>AgentGraph: risk_audit decision
    AgentGraph-->>StreamlitApp: pause before settlement

    StreamlitApp->>User: show approval UI
    User->>StreamlitApp: approve release
    StreamlitApp->>AgentGraph: resume graph

    AgentGraph->>Tools: xrpl_settlement_node()
    Tools->>XRPL: submit payment
    XRPL-->>Tools: tx_hash
    Tools->>Webhook: send delivery notification
    Webhook-->>Tools: webhook success
    Tools-->>AgentGraph: settlement result

    AgentGraph-->>StreamlitApp: workflow completed
    StreamlitApp->>SQLiteDB: record transaction row
    StreamlitApp-->>User: show merchant history updated